      <div>

      </div>

  school: string;
}> {
  render() {
    const oneTeam = this.props;
    return <div>{oneTeam.school}</div>;
  }
}

function AllTeams() {
  return (
    <div>
      <h4>List of All teams</h4>
      {Teams.map((oneTeam) => (

    </div>
  );
}

function Teamlist() {
  return (
    <div>
      <h3>Information about the teams</h3>
      {Teams.map((oneTeam) => (
        <Team {...oneTeam} />
      ))}

  );
}
